## 7. Restrictions

Where heritage assets are subject to restrictions on disposal, use, or location (donor restrictions, legal protection, repatriation claims, customary or community restrictions), these restrictions are recorded against the asset in the heritage register and are disclosed individually in Note (see register).

## 8. Insurance and conservation

The carrying amount of heritage assets does not include amounts attributable to insurance or replacement cost. Insurance values and conservation requirements are tracked separately on the heritage register.

